Package borehole.gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoreHoleGUI
    Main class for the User interface for camera module project.
    Data
    The data class is a storage box class that let the different threads change and retrieve the different data.
    DataLogger
    This class creates a text file and logs the data every second.
    DrillFrame
    Main frame for GUI application Runs as a thread and obersvable to update data and video whenever change is applied to data class
    ImagePanel
    This class is an extended version of JPanel.
    ImageToVideo
    This class converts buffered image to a video file.
    ImageUtils  
    SerialReceiver
    Handles serial connection on the USB port, establish connection, extract data by plug and play
    TCP
    Client class that handles the connection to the server, retrieves the data stream and send commands to the server
    UDP
    This class processes incoming images from a DatagramPacket.
